        <item>
            <title>1.1.0</title>
            <pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 22:59:17 +0900</pubDate>
            <link>https://github.com/Saqoosha/Canopy</link>
            <sparkle:version>5</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.1.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <sparkle:hardwareRequirements>arm64</sparkle:hardwareRequirements>
            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[### Features
- Added Preferences window (⌘,) with 4 settings:
  - Default permission mode for new sessions
  - Automatic update check toggle
  - Max recent directories in launcher
  - Default working directory

### Bug Fixes
- Fixed context usage bar in status bar showing incorrect fill level — the bar now accurately reflects the displayed percentage
- Fixed Sparkle update window inheriting the main window size instead of using its own default size
]]></description>
